mainText:
People like Steve change history .... Not only do part of it, they dictate how history should be written ..... miss him ... I never met him in person .... but his creativity has invaded and changed the world including my life .....
 His dicipulos has an obligation to continue writing this story and keep the constant change and evolution proposed by him ...
 His greatest quality was to be bold and creative .... His greatest fault was to be bold and creative ...... Rest in Peace &nbsp;
